This is Perl module Moxy::Plugin::Tidy.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - Moxy::Plugin::Tidy

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
Moxy::Plugin::Tidy:

    $ cpanm Moxy::Plugin::Tidy

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Moxy-Plugin-Tidy-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Moxy-Plugin-Tidy-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Moxy::Plugin::Tidy documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Moxy::Plugin::Tidy

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

